-- Aluminium Bahrain to Raise Smelter Capacity by 400,000 Tons, CEO Says
-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 2010-09-21T07:06:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/aluminium-bahrain-to-raise-smelter-capacity-by-400-000-tons-ceo-says.html
Aluminium Bahrain BSC, which runs a
smelter on the island nation in the Persian Gulf, said it plans
to expand capacity at the 850,000-metric-ton-a-year plant.  Capacity will grow by 400,000 tons in the “coming
years,” Chief Executive Officer Laurent Schmitt said at a
conference in Bahrain.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Tuttle in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net  